data.description: Beautiful and well maintained  farmhouse design, minutes to 985 and 85, close to Lake Lanier, walking distance to downtown Flowery Branch Historic District, Resort style amenities including clubhouse, firepit, playground, pavilion, park, and large swimming pool. This home boasts large gourmet kitchen w/white cabinets, beveled subway tile backsplash & granite countertops, large island opens to casual dining and great room, 4 Bedrooms and 2.5 bath. Crown molding on main. Tile and granite in primary bath. DO NOT MISS THIS OPORTUNITY!!
